data.description:
This beautiful property is now even more enticing with MOTIVATED SELLERS reducing sales price to $399,000.00
This home has already been appraised and surpasses our list price of $430,000, making it an absolute steal. 
This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem is nestled in a quiet and highly desirable neighborhood. 

The master suite is a true oasis, offering ample space for relaxation and tranquility. Upstairs, the second floor boasts a versatile game room that can easily double as an office space, catering to all your needs.
 Additionally, you'll find three bedrooms with a Jack and Jill bathroom, ideal for family living.
With its generous layout, serene surroundings, and convenient location, this property truly encapsulates the perfect blend of comfort and convenience for a growing family.
